 ‚Ėź‚Ėą‚Ėą ‚ĖĎ   a provincial orphan whose destructive behaviour precipitates     ‚ĖĎ ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ĖĆ
 ‚Ėź‚Ėą‚Ėą ‚ĖĎ   his relocation from the home of a long-term foster family        ‚ĖĎ ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ĖĆ
 ‚Ėź‚Ėą‚Ėą ‚ĖĎ   to the care of a benevolent elderly couple. In the course        ‚ĖĎ ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ĖĆ
 ‚Ėź‚Ėą‚Ėą ‚ĖĎ   of this transition, Pialats film presents the turbulence         ‚ĖĎ ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ĖĆ
 ‚Ėź‚Ėą‚Ėą ‚ĖĎ   of Francois' unmoored existence, and his explosive               ‚ĖĎ ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ĖĆ
